Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:54.96,tari-----STAFF,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,710)}日听：月長石  翻译：花解语 中校：散仙\N 日校：冷漠的风  时间轴：我见青山 压制：エロ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:38.48,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到胸中澎湃的声音时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.57,0:00:43.75,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,起跑线就出现在你的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:46.35,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,虽是一条看不见的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:49.91,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,也要开始奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.14,0:00:52.02,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,这样总比放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:55.25,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,更加让人着迷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.43,0:01:00.23,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,不安总在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.29,0:01:06.10,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,阻挡着自由的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:09.48,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,超越现在 迈出步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:12.14,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,把光明撒向那未知的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:17.72,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,在最初的轮回中 找到通往明天的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:23.71,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,前进中的我们怀有无尽的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.80,0:01:29.52,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,要相信闪耀的自我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.75,0:01:35.16,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,将永不放弃的力量用最大的爱包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.39,0:01:37.88,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,开始我们的旅程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.99,0:01:43.98,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,走向那崭新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:01:59.71,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}居然在这种时候眼前漆黑一片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.23,0:02:02.23,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}难道说到此为止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:03.96,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:06.74,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还有 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:11.25,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:16.54,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 现在正是解放这个力量的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:26.36,tari--SUB-m-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}凝聚大家希望的这柄剑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:28.09,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,全国大赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.09,0:02:30.84,tari--SUB-m-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}无上荣光的holy blade
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:32.06,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,紧张吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.86,0:02:36.96,tari--SUB-m-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}将勇气 将泪水 全都化作力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.83,0:02:35.80,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 一直在脑海中模拟这个情形 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.20,0:02:43.83,tari--SUB-m-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}现在 去迎战强大的敌人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:41.72,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  我也想站在这么大的舞台上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.36,0:02:44.05,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 弓道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:51.52,tari--SUB-m-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Forever Forever Forever Forever
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:46.75,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我是说马
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.44,0:02:48.06,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,马？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:51.41,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我想成为骑手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:55.72,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,和全力奔跑的马一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:57.89,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,比任何人都先冲过终点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:01.45,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 很帅嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.85,0:03:02.60,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:05.47,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  别太闹腾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:08.27,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,而且还没到恭喜的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:09.78,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,这才比赛第一回合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.01,0:03:14.05,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是要你抱着必胜的气势去拼搏啊 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:15.15,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:17.38,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,你想让维恩白忙活一场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:19.92,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,那么那些异想天开的构思算怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:26.24,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:29.92,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起来加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:32.65,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,给 和奏的沙球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:43.03,tari--SUB-m-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}现在 去迎战强大的敌人吧 嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:49.46,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我今天身体不太舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.57,0:03:50.79,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:07.12,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,是闹过头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:09.58,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,来夏很喜欢庆典嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:10.55,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,庆典？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:15.15,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,呐 田中开始打羽球的契机是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.01,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,别用简称
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:21.99,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}白浜坂高校 田中大智选手 请到指定的比赛场地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:24.27,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 奋起一搏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:26.37,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:27.95,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,大智 准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.57,0:04:30.20,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}这是江户时代民众起义时所用的口号
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:29.68,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.38,0:04:33.59,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}带着必死的觉悟把一整杯满载荣耀的酒水给…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.06,0:04:35.48,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,来夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:40.31,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:43.74,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:46.43,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,来了 请慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:49.49,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,来了 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:51.77,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,这个 有粉色的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:56.56,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,粉色 啊 只有这里的这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:58.56,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,红色的也不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:01.07,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:04.93,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 欢迎回来 今天真早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:05.83,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:08.31,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就要这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:09.37,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:12.42,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 能给我倒杯茶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:14.31,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,请稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.97,0:05:16.89,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我来做晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:18.37,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.96,0:05:21.29,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请到这边来付钱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:43.01,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,胜方 和田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:55.17,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,前八名的话 已经够厉害了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:55.78,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:06:00.00,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果是前四名的话就可以在全国大赛上出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:02.03,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.14,0:06:05.15,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,田中 好慢呐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:07.61,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:10.70,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,那顺便买瓶绿茶回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:13.83,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,请您走好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:15.53,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我拿一下包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:28.00,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,在哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:31.00,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,谁哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:33.35,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,只是在脑中做模拟训练而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:35.20,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在记忆犹新
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:37.86,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,已经 不想再输了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:40.86,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,晴香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:44.90,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,田中是从什么时候开始打网球的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:48.78,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大概是小学三年级开始的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:51.26,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我开始社团活动后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:55.10,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,大智没多久就说「我也要去」 还想要自己的球拍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:56.34,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:59.36,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,小学就开始打了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:02.46,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不去羽毛球更加盛行的高中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.36,0:07:06.90,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 白高的话 可以骑自行车上学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.31,0:07:09.25,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,以前部员也更多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.88,0:07:11.80,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我有个仰慕的选手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.66,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,也是我们高中出身的… 之类的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:18.61,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是因为有那位选手才开始打羽球的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:19.85,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,叫你别用简称了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:25.45,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:26.80,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.03,0:07:28.24,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:32.22,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,为了夏天也能避免着凉所以有热的卖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:35.06,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么呀这
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:36.57,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:38.67,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 纱羽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:41.78,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,和奏她没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:44.49,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,最近有点无精打采的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:45.80,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.32,0:08:00.40,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 水好冰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:01.03,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:01.95,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,和奏酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.09,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.16,0:08:07.09,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 纱羽的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:09.20,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,是志保哦 疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:11.38,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,久违地闯祸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:17.27,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:19.08,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,对纱羽要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:22.39,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 动不动就要说「你已经不年轻了」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:24.92,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,真是一年比一年神气了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.51,0:08:27.47,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,你们 感情真好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.90,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,好热…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.05,0:08:40.94,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 在那边随便放下就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.43,0:08:43.58,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,出了很多汗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.90,0:08:45.02,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要泡个澡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:47.75,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 啊 不用了 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:48.93,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:53.08,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 你稍微等下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:56.69,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,是这个吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:00.01,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.07,0:09:02.06,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:04.41,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是白校毕业的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.59,0:09:06.14,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,算是和奏酱的前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:06.80,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:09.30,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,以前这一带呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.30,0:09:12.05,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,不是上白高就是上镰高的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:14.27,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,看 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:16.21,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,是和奏的妈妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:17.42,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,真昼学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:21.28,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.53,0:09:24.44,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 她比我大一级
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:26.86,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是高仓学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:30.35,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,高仓直子 现在是教导主任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.60,0:09:31.50,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:36.29,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你复印一份完整的 下回来拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.20,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:41.41,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候大家 都是合唱团的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:45.06,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,是哦 在大赛取得优胜后拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.99,0:09:47.41,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,没听你妈妈说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:55.71,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,病情都没跟她说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:10:00.13,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 那孩子不是备考嘛 就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:01.42,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:04.47,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:06.48,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,那个我来弄就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:12.59,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:21.55,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 今天的晚饭要我来做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:24.25,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 啊 那就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:26.87,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,你今天很闲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:29.17,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 没有 很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.35,0:10:34.16,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.16,0:10:35.20,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:38.58,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,听说妈妈昏倒真是吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:41.65,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,那是大家夸大其词了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:45.94,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,这回也很快就能出院了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.59,0:10:49.57,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我去换条抹布回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:54.87,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 要好好爱惜身体哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:59.52,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,和和奏一起写歌的话 说不定就可以好起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:05.84,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,来 让我听听和奏的点子和意见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:08.14,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说没时间干那种事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.57,0:11:10.44,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要参加考试了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.43,0:11:12.92,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,那一起唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:16.10,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,没那个心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:21.72,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,火气太大会影响实力发挥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:24.61,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为是谁的错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:29.62,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,惹你生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:31.94,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:37.00,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,一起写歌的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:39.79,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,就能好起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:49.88,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你能不能好好教啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.26,0:11:52.11,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,这根本不是什么练习曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.59,0:11:56.11,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,你小时候就经常这样和我一起唱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:57.41,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.41,0:12:03.57,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然学习也很重要 但考试会结束 音乐却会持续哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.34,0:12:07.21,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,为了音乐能一直伴随和奏左右
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:09.82,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,千万不要忘记 爱着音乐的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:10.48,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:15.04,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,学校都考不上的话说这些还有什么意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.66,0:12:33.24,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,闪着腰了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:37.10,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 那么星期六你去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:38.86,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我就星期一开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.95,0:12:42.72,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 这种事就要大家互相关照嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:46.22,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,好 那么再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:48.86,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,远野的叔叔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:51.43,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 又是腰出问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:55.04,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,下周一我打算去田里帮下忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:55.60,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:13:00.30,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,秀彦是上班族似乎请不了急假
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:03.48,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,但是大概要去两三天 你没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:05.89,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,真是 我也不是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:08.94,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭 要不要叫寿司呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.07,0:13:10.04,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:18.73,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.14,0:13:19.88,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:24.71,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,房间里的钢琴 我想处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:25.32,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:28.52,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经用不着了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:32.65,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,如果交给真正喜欢音乐的人使用的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:35.34,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,想必妈妈也会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:37.34,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:40.21,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,CD只要有个小收录机就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:42.92,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,其它用不着的东西也处理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:45.40,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,腾出来的地方放张床什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:47.68,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:50.27,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,那我明天打电话问问
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:51.83,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:05.19,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,关东地区今晨云层开始扩散
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.43,0:14:09.97,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,目前强烈低气压正自小笠原群岛近海北上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:14.46,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,受其影响午后至傍晚的天气将可能十分恶劣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:26.10,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 会补习到很晚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:27.77,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,还是带上雨衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.38,0:14:30.01,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,风好像也越来越强了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:31.25,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:34.07,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:38.04,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,今天会有人来拿钢琴和其它那些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:42.30,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我会整理清楚的 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.57,0:14:43.34,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.20,0:15:00.69,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:03.37,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:04.37,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,金鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:05.61,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,是鲸鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.62,0:15:08.72,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,是金鱼啦 金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:09.58,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,鲸鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:11.07,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:12.76,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,是鲸鱼啦 鲸鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:13.55,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,是金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:16.98,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,那 折中一下当它是海豚先生好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:20.50,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,海豚先生在唱歌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.79,0:15:21.79,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:44.08,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:46.90,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 我也三点半就走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:49.02,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事就给我打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:52.06,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔那里手机信号不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:53.94,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,不过远野的电话你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:56.49,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭可以叫寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:58.52,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,说了我不会有事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:15:59.71,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,你走好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:02.08,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:39.29,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:42.99,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,今天待会儿有社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:44.68,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:48.45,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,为了庆祝大智进入前八强 要开派对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:55.47,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 今天想在下雨之前买好东西回家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:06.14,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:10.13,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始羽毛球大赛的庆功宴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:11.44,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,田中请客哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:14.33,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 今天有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.60,0:17:17.73,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 可是蛋糕也买了和奏那份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:19.47,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,有很大草莓的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:21.21,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,就来吃一下蛋糕也行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:23.26,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:30.82,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,果然 没什么精神呐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:33.66,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,不会是讨厌草莓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.87,0:17:34.81,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,没那可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.31,0:17:37.50,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,难道是 我太烦人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.06,0:17:40.97,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,这倒是有点可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:54.58,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:35.01,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,小龙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:42.37,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,小龙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:46.00,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,小龙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.32,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.83,0:19:08.97,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 妈妈 不是叫你帮我把雨衣拿出来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:11.79,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉 现在就帮你拿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:12.98,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:17.83,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,自己的东西自己准备好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:19.75,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,准考证带了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:20.66,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,带了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.24,0:19:23.02,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,没有忘了东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:24.33,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.37,0:19:26.33,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,那就走好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:28.19,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:33.09,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,小龙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:38.55,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,和奏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:42.07,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:44.68,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,这个 可别忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:48.29,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西又无所谓的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:50.66,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,会淋湿的 赶快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.76,0:20:21.87,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,今后的路想和女儿… 和和奏一起走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.69,0:20:27.49,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,不管健康的时候还是生病的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.39,0:20:31.93,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,高兴的时候还是悲伤的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:37.71,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,那样的歌 感觉和和奏一起就能写出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.83,0:20:44.18,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,因为对我来说 歌曲是传达爱的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:51.20,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,是和奏教会了我重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:56.32,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,想要对她传达的感情便化成了歌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.18,0:20:59.59,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能够一起唱出这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.37,0:21:05.80,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,如果能够听到来自和奏的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.71,0:21:12.43,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生 就太圆满了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.74,0:21:29.87,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,还没说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.61,0:21:32.80,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,「我出门了」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:35.71,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,「对不起」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:39.03,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,还有「谢谢」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.96,0:21:46.54,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,再也不能一起唱歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:22:01.95,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.95,0:22:24.16,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,无论是晴天还是雨天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.30,0:22:30.98,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你们在身边 我总能露出笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.23,0:22:36.88,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,直到记忆的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.31,0:22:44.54,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,倾听记忆中摇晃的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:50.88,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,来  把手递给我 与我们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.88,0:22:58.80,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,在不是一个人的空间里 尽情欢乐的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.20,0:23:04.53,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,愉快的风吹拂过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.57,0:23:11.84,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,有时欢笑有时哭泣有时放声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.48,0:23:17.65,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,接着敞开自己的心扉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.86,0:23:29.80,tari--OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,轻哼记忆里的旋律 奏响乐章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.73,0:23:42.98,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,和奏 不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.98,0:23:46.05,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,和奏 你觉得我们首先最需要的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.05,0:23:46.77,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.83,0:23:48.57,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}喂 和奏 接下来有空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.06,0:23:49.87,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.60,0:00:06.73,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,我带了一个可靠的伙伴 来代替我守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:07.94,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.95,tari--SUB-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,红钢铁战士 登场
